  "title": "Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Develop and implement data-driven online marketing campaigns (ecommerce, SEA, SEO, email automation campaigns and social media) that generate revenue growth, lead generation and brand awareness</li>\n  <li>Manage, develop and execute promotional activities that will support the company and clients’ targets</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the sales team to plan and manage their communication, promotional and marketing needs</li>\n  <li>Localize marketing communications and collaterals for campaigns, events, promotions and activities</li>\n  <li>Oversee and scheduling marketing campaigns across both owned platforms and paid channels</li>\n  <li>Evaluate and explore new online marketing trends and platforms</li>\n  <li>Conduct market research and customer surveys to assess demand and brand positioning</li>\n  <li>Provide copywriting support for marketing collaterals</li>\n  <li>To track, evaluate and report results and effectiveness of marketing campaigns</li>\n  <li>Accountable for all digital marketing related projects and operational tasks from creative visual design, content development, launch to maintenance and continuous improvement</li>\n  <li>Occasional hosting of live streaming is needed</li>\n</ul>",
